@startuml US-04
title US-04 View Game Details

actor User
boundary "Web UI" as UI
control "GameController" as GC
control "GameService" as GS
database "GameRepository" as GR
database "DeveloperRepository" as DR
database "GenreRepository" as GeR

User -> UI: Click game title
UI -> GC: GET /games/{id}
GC -> GS: getGameDetails(id)
GS -> GR: findById(id)
GR --> GS: game
GS -> DR: findById(game.developerId)
DR --> GS: developer
GS -> GeR: findGenresByGameId(id)
GeR --> GS: genres
GS --> GC: details(title, desc, price, releaseDate, developerName, genres)
GC --> UI: 200 OK + details
UI --> User: Show details page
@enduml
